                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-573-18520510 t18520510-573-punishment-88"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Maule.</hi>
